  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposal, by reason of excessive alterations, loss of original fabric and introduction of significant internal walls, would detract from the historic character of the locally listed building, to the detriment of the special significance of the host building. As such the proposal is contrary to policy LP4 (Non Designated Heritage Assets) of the Hackney Local Plan 2020.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposal, by reason of inappropriate layout and design, would provide substandard residential accommodation, to the detriment of the residential amenities of future occupiers of the residential units. As such the proposal is contrary to policies D4 (Delivering good design) and D6 (Housing quality and standards) of the London Plan (2021), policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP17 (Housing Design) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020) and the recommendations of the Supplementary Planning Guidance: Housing 2006.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The applicant has failed to provide suitable marketing information, which should have included the potential subdivision of the existing commercial floorspace. The proposal would therefore result in the unjustified loss of office floorspace, to the detriment of the provision of office floorspace in the borough. As such the proposal is contrary to policies SD1 (Opportunity Areas) and E1 (Offices) of the London Plan (2021), policy LP27 (Protecting and Promoting Office Floorspace in the Borough) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020), and the recommendations of the City Fringe Opportunity Area Planning Framework 2015.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;"
  ],
